OL,3,CFarage vows to freeze immigration as
OL,4,Che unveils Reform's core pledges
OL,6,FThe party leader also acknowledged
OL,7,Fthat Reform UK would not form the next
OL,8,Fgovernment after the July 4 election.
OL,10,FSpeaking in South Wales on Monday, he
OL,11,Fsaid the party is "not pretending"
OL,12,Fthat Reform UK will win, due to it
OL,13,Fbeing "a very, very new political
OL,14,Fparty".
OL,16,FBut he did say he has his sights on
OL,17,Fthe next General Election.
OL,19,F"Although this election is for our
OL,20,Fparty, and for me, the first important
OL,21,Fstep on the road to 2029."
