OL,3,CFarage vows to freeze immigration as
OL,4,Che unveils Reform's core pledges
OL,6,FThe party says that imposing strict
OL,7,Flimits on people coming to the UK is
OL,8,Fthe only way to relieve pressure on
OL,9,Fhousing and public services, and to
OL,10,F"protect our culture".
OL,12,FIt says "essential skills, mainly
OL,13,Faround healthcare" would be the only
OL,14,Fexception to migration - but does not
OL,15,Fprovide a conclusive list as to what
OL,16,Fexactly constitutes an "essential"
OL,17,Fskill.
