OL,3,CFarage vows to freeze immigration as
OL,4,Che unveils Reform's core pledges
OL,6,FThe manifesto also pledged to "stop
OL,7,Fthe boats" with a four-point plan,
OL,8,Fwhich includes "picking up illegal
OL,9,Fmigrants out of boats and taking them
OL,10,Fback to France".
OL,12,FThey added that migrants could be
OL,13,Fprocessed offshore "if necessary". It
OL,14,Fhas also said there will be "no legal
OL,15,Faid" for non-citizens arriving in the
OL,16,Fcountry and that those rejected "will
OL,17,Fbe returned".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
