OL,4,Che unveils Reform's core pledges
OL,6,FThere would also be "immediate
OL,7,Fdeportation" for foreign criminals at
OL,8,Fthe end of their prison sentences and
OL,9,Fimmigrants who commit a crime would
OL,10,Fhave their citizenship withdrawn.
OL,12,FReform UK says it would lift the
OL,13,Fincome tax threshold to #20,000,
OL,14,Fmeaning people would not start paying
OL,15,Ftax on their salary until they were
OL,16,Fearning more than that figure - it
OL,17,Fcurrently stands at #12,570.
OL,19,FThe party claims this would stop seven
OL,20,Fmillion people from paying income tax.
