OL,6,FThe party also wants to change how
OL,7,Fbusinesses are taxed, with plans to
OL,8,Flift the minimum profit threshold to
OL,9,F#100,000. It says that would "free
OL,10,Fover 1.2 million small and medium
OL,11,Fsized businesses from corporation tax".
OL,13,FIt wants to lift the VAT threshold to
OL,14,F#150,000, which would be an increase
OL,15,Ffrom the current #90,000 limit that
OL,16,Fcame into place in April.
